      <title>陷入困境的杂草股考验着华尔街对 2024 年反弹的信心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/floundering-weed-stocks-test-wall-street-s-faith-in-2024-rebound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从理论上讲，投资大麻公司的理由是有史以来最强烈的。大麻店疯狂地出现在美国各地的街角，而 2024 年总统大选也为毒品改革提供了动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/floundering-weed-stocks-test-wall-street-s-faith-in-2024-rebound</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
